@node c "How to register MagicEditor if you live in any other part of the world"

The fee to register MagicFile/MagicEditor is US$25,- (US dollars), you can
send it to me in a few different ways:

 - cash in an envelope (possibly by registered mail)
 - international money order (of 35,- dutch guilders)
 - eurocheck (of 35,- dutch guilders)

NO other kind of checks please or bank transfers because it will cost me a
lot of money to cash them at my bank's.

@{b}You must always send me the registration.form (found in the archive),
correctly filled in, through e-mail/netmail or normal post!!@{ub}

You can find my address if you click @{"here" link bbs}

When I have received the money I'll crash the key to your fidonet number,
if you don't have one you can download the key at my bbs.
@endnode
